Oh, shit!

547
00:30:59,733 --> 00:31:01,066
What the hell are you doing?

548
00:31:01,566 --> 00:31:02,600
Oh, Erng!

549
00:31:02,810 --> 00:31:04,663
(he's imitating the sounds of the drum)

550
00:31:05,466 --> 00:31:07,466
My ears are about to burst.

551
00:31:07,866 --> 00:31:08,866
Wake up!

552
00:31:13,966 --> 00:31:14,966
What is wrong with you?

553
00:31:15,996 --> 00:31:16,996
Oh, shit!

554
00:31:18,264 --> 00:31:19,350
Serves you right.

555
00:31:19,578 --> 00:31:20,738
It's all because of you, Hia.

556
00:31:23,777 --> 00:31:24,777
Move!

557
00:31:26,255 --> 00:31:27,494
Where's my morning kiss?

558
00:31:35,300 --> 00:31:37,566
Who's going to kiss you
with that morning breath?

559
00:31:37,866 --> 00:31:38,866
It's not that bad.

560
00:31:39,566 --> 00:31:41,466
Why did you wake up so early today?

561
00:31:42,766 --> 00:31:43,766
Well...

562
00:31:46,133 --> 00:31:47,400
I had a dream last night.

563
00:31:48,100 --> 00:31:49,100
Hmm?

564
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:51,000
What did you dream about?

565
00:31:53,066 --> 00:31:54,866
I dreamed that you took me on a trip.

566
00:31:58,133 --> 00:31:59,133
Where to?

567
00:32:01,097 --> 00:32:03,503
Ummmm

568
00:32:05,366 --> 00:32:06,366
Hell.

569
00:32:07,933 --> 00:32:08,933
Aww

570
00:32:08,966 --> 00:32:10,766
I already take you there every day.

571
00:32:10,933 --> 00:32:11,933
Ow!

572
00:32:12,133 --> 00:32:13,366
Seriously, where?

573
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:15,000
Well...

574
00:32:16,566 --> 00:32:17,566
The beach.

575
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:19,800
Where?

576
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:21,147
Koh Samet?

577
00:32:21,421 --> 00:32:24,056
Where everyone gets bedded!

578
00:32:24,117 --> 00:32:26,176
(a famous line that Thai people will
say when talking about this island)

579
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:27,200
Uh...

580
00:32:28,166 --> 00:32:29,800
Whoa, almost.

581
00:32:32,100 --> 00:32:32,900
Hey.

582
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:33,400
Huh?

583
00:32:33,401 --> 00:32:34,500
Then let's go there.

584
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:42,500
Hey kiddo, my hubby is taking me on a trip!

585
00:32:53,866 --> 00:32:55,466
Erng, your phone.

586
00:33:19,037 --> 00:33:21,324
Erng, want to meet up?

587
00:33:30,871 --> 00:33:32,095
Where?

588
00:33:32,369 --> 00:33:33,533
The usual place.

589
00:33:38,375 --> 00:33:39,807
What the hell is "the usual place"?

590
00:33:45,334 --> 00:33:46,694
Fine. See you in half an hour.

591
00:34:02,333 --> 00:34:03,515
Weren't you going to help?

592
00:34:03,516 --> 00:34:04,516
No.

593
00:34:04,966 --> 00:34:06,647
Nok, it's your job.

594
00:34:06,648 --> 00:34:07,166
I'm not doing it.

595
00:34:07,466 --> 00:34:08,946
Then why don't you do it and take it?

596
00:34:09,066 --> 00:34:09,866
I don't want to.

597
00:34:10,000 --> 00:34:11,910
Then why did you come here?

598
00:34:11,911 --> 00:34:12,911
I came...

599
00:34:14,813 --> 00:34:15,978
to bring you spicy salad.

600
00:34:15,979 --> 00:34:17,069
I thought you said you'd help.

601
00:34:17,070 --> 00:34:18,705
I'm feeling lazy.

602
00:34:19,298 --> 00:34:20,000
Take it.

603
00:34:20,001 --> 00:34:21,094
No.

604
00:34:21,095 --> 00:34:22,095
Hurry up.

605
00:34:24,933 --> 00:34:25,647
Come on.

606
00:34:25,647 --> 00:34:26,322
You want a piece of me?

607
00:34:26,322 --> 00:34:26,822
Nok!

608
00:34:26,823 --> 00:34:28,663
Just wait until my Hia
gets here. You're dead.

609
00:34:29,736 --> 00:34:30,394
Why?

610
00:34:30,395 --> 00:34:31,708
Hia!

611
00:34:31,709 --> 00:34:32,709
Help!

612
00:34:34,490 --> 00:34:35,490
In.

613
00:34:37,300 --> 00:34:38,300
What's wrong?

614
00:34:41,709 --> 00:34:43,668
In-In, Nok-Nok are hurting.

615
00:34:43,669 --> 00:34:45,669
My wrists hurt so much.

616
00:34:49,733 --> 00:34:50,933
What did your friend say?

617
00:35:00,900 --> 00:35:02,206
Oh, Hia.

618
00:35:03,028 --> 00:35:04,645
My neck hurts so much.

619
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:07,133
Let me see.

620
00:35:07,500 --> 00:35:08,733
It's all red.

621
00:35:09,733 --> 00:35:10,733
Let me take a look.

622
00:35:11,666 --> 00:35:12,666
Look, Hia

623
00:35:12,866 --> 00:35:13,853
You'll be fine.

624
00:35:13,853 --> 00:35:14,853
Ouch!

625
00:35:17,466 --> 00:35:18,466
Ouch, it hurts!

626
00:35:19,000 --> 00:35:19,800
Ouch!

627
00:35:19,933 --> 00:35:20,733
Look, In.

628
00:35:20,766 --> 00:35:23,766
Ouch, my wrists hurt so much too.

629
00:35:24,733 --> 00:35:25,733
Hey!

630
00:35:25,819 --> 00:35:26,819
What is this, Hia?

631
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:35,600
I'm going out for a bit.

632
00:35:35,766 --> 00:35:36,766
I'll be right back.

633
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:38,000
Where are you going?

634
00:35:39,333 --> 00:35:40,808
I rented an amulet.

635
00:35:41,036 --> 00:35:42,594
I forgot I had to pick it up today.

636
00:35:43,066 --> 00:35:45,600
Ah, no wonder you're
dressed like this today.

637
00:35:46,533 --> 00:35:47,774
I wanted to look decent.

638
00:35:48,048 --> 00:35:49,840
To match the sacred vibe.

639
00:35:56,066 --> 00:35:57,066
I'm off then.

640
00:36:06,566 --> 00:36:07,066
Nok!

641
00:36:07,066 --> 00:36:07,666
What?

642
00:36:07,866 --> 00:36:08,866
Where are you going?

643
00:36:14,766 --> 00:36:15,766
Bom-Bom.

644
00:36:17,466 --> 00:36:18,466
Shit.

645
00:36:19,500 --> 00:36:21,533
Why did I make his name sound cute?

646
00:36:23,266 --> 00:36:24,266
So annoying.

647
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:27,533
Nok, you again?

648
00:36:27,666 --> 00:36:30,533
I was trying to wipe your face!
Do you want me to wipe it that badly?

649
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:31,804
Let me go, Nok!

650
00:36:31,804 --> 00:36:32,400
No!

651
00:36:32,566 --> 00:36:34,242
You're always trying to
hit on your friend's guy.

652
00:36:34,266 --> 00:36:35,266
Because he's handsome!

653
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:39,000
Nok!

654
00:36:54,066 --> 00:36:55,066
Surprise!

655
00:36:55,866 --> 00:36:57,200
Surprise, my ass!

656
00:36:57,700 --> 00:36:58,700
Why is it you?

657
00:36:59,933 --> 00:37:00,733
Yeah.

658
00:37:00,933 --> 00:37:01,933
It's me.

659
00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:04,200
Surprised?

660
00:37:09,133 --> 00:37:11,076
Let's take this outside, one-on-one.

661
00:37:11,100 --> 00:37:12,166
What are you doing?

662
00:37:13,700 --> 00:37:14,700
Don't tell me...

663
00:37:15,133 --> 00:37:17,466
you called my boyfriend
to get back together.

664
00:37:19,466 --> 00:37:20,466
Mind your own business.

665
00:37:22,766 --> 00:37:24,133
I can't do that.

666
00:37:26,900 --> 00:37:28,933
Because you messed with my wife first.

667
00:37:30,700 --> 00:37:32,660
Taking this outside like
you said is a good idea.

668
00:37:33,600 --> 00:37:35,960
Didn't you learn your lesson
after I beat you up last time?

669
00:37:37,333 --> 00:37:38,400
You think I'm scared?

670
00:37:38,766 --> 00:37:39,566
Pee Bom!

671
00:37:39,566 --> 00:37:40,566
Aten!

672
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:41,800
Why did you do this?

673
00:37:42,333 --> 00:37:43,773
I told you I'm breaking up with you.

674
00:37:43,900 --> 00:37:44,466
I'm not breaking up.

675
00:37:44,467 --> 00:37:45,776
If we break up, you'll
just go back to P'Erng.

676
00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:47,000
Well, Erng is better than you.

677
00:37:47,100 --> 00:37:48,620
When you wanted to break up with Erng,

678
00:37:49,333 --> 00:37:50,333
you said I was better.

679
00:37:50,600 --> 00:37:52,400
Why are you going back on your word now?

680
00:37:52,666 --> 00:37:53,900
Because I finally woke up!

681
00:37:54,500 --> 00:37:55,600
Get lost!

682
00:37:56,500 --> 00:37:57,500
Shit!

683
00:37:57,766 --> 00:37:59,055
He hit him with a wrench!

684
00:37:59,056 --> 00:38:00,056
Hey, Pee Ten!

685
00:38:00,300 --> 00:38:01,533
Hey, calm down!

686
00:38:02,166 --> 00:38:03,566
Calm down!

687
00:38:03,866 --> 00:38:04,866
Calm down.

688
00:38:10,533 --> 00:38:11,866
Do you think he's dead?

689
00:38:22,466 --> 00:38:27,066
Is this the hospital? Someone is dying.
Please come here quickly.

690
00:38:47,500 --> 00:38:50,266
Erng, sorry that I lied.

691
00:39:16,500 --> 00:39:17,500
Erng.

692
00:39:18,500 --> 00:39:19,732
Where are you?

693
00:39:20,280 --> 00:39:21,280
Stay right there.

694
00:39:21,863 --> 00:39:22,863
I'm coming to you.

695
00:39:32,133 --> 00:39:35,278
Come on in. We have 9 likes and 16 shares.

696
00:39:35,279 --> 00:39:39,533
Because if you like it 10
times, it won't register.

697
00:39:41,100 --> 00:39:42,235
Luang Pu Khem. (a
legendary Thai comedy meme)

698
00:39:42,259 --> 00:39:44,259
Giving away Luang Pu Khem
from Nong E-Tong Temple.

699
00:39:44,520 --> 00:39:47,038
Consecrated by the monk himself.

700
00:39:47,063 --> 00:39:50,539
Moving on to the next one.
Wow, this gives me goosebumps.

701
00:39:51,039 --> 00:39:51,722
Erng.

702
00:39:52,039 --> 00:39:53,039
In.

703
00:39:53,933 --> 00:39:54,933
What are you doing?

704
00:39:56,733 --> 00:39:57,733
I'm sorry.

705
00:39:58,100 --> 00:39:58,977
Huh?

706
00:39:58,978 --> 00:40:00,966
Do you think you deserve forgiveness?

707
00:40:01,300 --> 00:40:02,300
I'm sorry.

708
00:40:09,100 --> 00:40:10,576
And why the hell are these guys here?

709
00:40:10,600 --> 00:40:12,333
Oh, look at this.

710
00:40:13,733 --> 00:40:14,733
Move.

711
00:40:14,872 --> 00:40:15,872
Nok!

712
00:40:17,266 --> 00:40:18,266
Yeah, go on in.

713
00:40:18,766 --> 00:40:20,100
Stop arguing.

714
00:40:20,466 --> 00:40:21,666
I'm going to the restroom.

715
00:40:23,166 --> 00:40:24,500
Go ahead. Go ahead.

716
00:40:28,966 --> 00:40:29,966
We barely survived that.

717
00:40:30,300 --> 00:40:31,300
You almost died.

718
00:40:44,500 --> 00:40:46,780
My 'package' got in the way

719
00:40:59,266 --> 00:41:00,266
Is he dead?

720
00:41:00,733 --> 00:41:01,500
No.

721
00:41:01,501 --> 00:41:03,133
Why didn't you just kill him?

722
00:41:03,566 --> 00:41:05,086
So I could attend his funeral instead.

723
00:41:05,133 --> 00:41:06,533
Pee Bom wanted to break up with me.

724
00:41:07,519 --> 00:41:09,253
He said he was going back to Pee Erng.

725
00:41:09,500 --> 00:41:10,866
So you cracked his head open?

726
00:41:11,600 --> 00:41:14,594
Remember this: what's easily stolen...

727
00:41:14,595 --> 00:41:16,600
can easily leave you too.

728
00:41:18,266 --> 00:41:20,333
Will you get back with Pee Bom?

729
00:41:20,933 --> 00:41:22,156
Sorry, babe.

730
00:41:22,841 --> 00:41:24,653
But this is my new man.

731
00:41:24,654 --> 00:41:28,100
The one who called the ambulance for Bom
before he died.

732
00:41:29,666 --> 00:41:31,566
Are you going to keep staring at him, In?

733
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:33,858
No way, I wasn't staring.

734
00:41:34,406 --> 00:41:36,133
You're accusing me again.

735
00:41:36,600 --> 00:41:37,570
Your new boyfriend?

736
00:41:37,570 --> 00:41:38,570
Yes.

737
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:40,000
Yes.

738
00:41:40,133 --> 00:41:40,900
What?

739
00:41:40,901 --> 00:41:42,266
I'm Pee Erng's new boyfriend.

740
00:41:43,300 --> 00:41:45,766
If there's nothing else,
we'll take our leave.

741
00:41:46,333 --> 00:41:47,766
I haven't eaten since noon.

742
00:41:49,733 --> 00:41:50,733
Let's go home.

743
00:41:50,800 --> 00:41:51,800
Yeah.

744
00:41:52,766 --> 00:41:53,554
Nok.

745
00:41:53,554 --> 00:41:54,054
Yeah?

746
00:41:54,300 --> 00:41:55,600
You can put your leg down now.

747
00:41:56,733 --> 00:41:59,200
Why didn't you tell me
sooner? My knee is sore.

748
00:42:12,466 --> 00:42:16,568
Aten, tell Bom
to stop bothering me.

749
00:42:17,299 --> 00:42:18,533
For someone like me,

750
00:42:19,500 --> 00:42:21,125
once I'm done, I'm done.

751
00:42:21,126 --> 00:42:22,126
Remember that.

752
00:42:23,533 --> 00:42:24,533
Let's go.

753
00:42:24,566 --> 00:42:25,566
Let's go home.

754
00:42:29,700 --> 00:42:32,566
Are you going to keep staring at Aten, Hia?

755
00:42:32,900 --> 00:42:35,900
Choose: do you want to sleep at home
or in the hospital like Bom?

756
00:42:39,700 --> 00:42:40,700
Home, please.

757
00:42:49,533 --> 00:42:50,533
You're screwed!

758
00:42:50,666 --> 00:42:52,266
Erng is in beast mode.

759
00:42:54,766 --> 00:42:56,533
Nok is asking what on earth just happened.

760
00:43:08,820 --> 00:43:09,820
Intha &amp; Akara

761
00:43:11,200 --> 00:43:12,924
Since I started dating In,

762
00:43:12,925 --> 00:43:15,400
my life feels like it's been thrown
into some crazy world.

763
00:43:16,100 --> 00:43:18,266
A world where my friends
think my boyfriend is cursed.

764
00:43:18,700 --> 00:43:21,180
When I walked back into the
shop and saw Erng holding a stick,

765
00:43:21,666 --> 00:43:23,266
I thought there was going to be a fight.

766
00:43:23,400 --> 00:43:25,900
Turns out he was just playing Harry Potter.

767
00:43:27,300 --> 00:43:28,333
But well,

768
00:43:29,600 --> 00:43:31,066
I'm secretly a bit happy...

769
00:43:31,566 --> 00:43:33,866
that everyone can see how much you love me.

770
00:43:36,466 --> 00:43:37,466
Of course I do.

771
00:43:37,566 --> 00:43:40,000
Otherwise, why would I
eat egg whites for you?

772
00:43:41,566 --> 00:43:43,500
Right now, it feels like a trial marriage.

773
00:43:46,266 --> 00:43:47,266
Eating together,

774
00:43:48,866 --> 00:43:50,026
going to the market together,

775
00:43:53,500 --> 00:43:55,393
sulking over the shop sign,

776
00:43:56,352 --> 00:43:58,110
and bickering over Bua Loy.

777
00:43:59,069 --> 00:44:03,666
We're like an old married
couple of ten years.

778
00:44:06,200 --> 00:44:08,100
Erng is so damn cute when he's jealous.

779
00:44:08,866 --> 00:44:11,366
Even if he hits me in
front of the whole market.

780
00:44:12,100 --> 00:44:14,133
But my favorite thing lately...

781
00:44:16,166 --> 00:44:18,300
is seeing Erng in his normal mode.

782
00:44:19,800 --> 00:44:21,200
When he picks the wrong vegetables,

783
00:44:21,600 --> 00:44:22,600
when he cooks,

784
00:44:23,400 --> 00:44:24,700
and when he plays the guitar.

785
00:44:28,366 --> 00:44:30,566
He's so cute, I don't know
what to do with myself.

786
00:44:33,266 --> 00:44:34,266
As for me,

787
00:44:35,600 --> 00:44:38,100
I just realized In has a childish side too.

788
00:44:39,300 --> 00:44:41,100
He gets happy when
he eats his favorite food,

789
00:44:45,100 --> 00:44:46,100
gets sulky easily,

790
00:44:48,566 --> 00:44:49,666
loves to be coddled,

791
00:44:52,066 --> 00:44:54,300
and is more head over
heels for me than normal.

792
00:44:56,100 --> 00:44:58,260
That day, my friend called
to tease me about the sign,

793
00:44:58,800 --> 00:45:00,366
saying my boyfriend has bad taste.

794
00:45:01,266 --> 00:45:02,966
At first, I thought it was just a joke.

795
00:45:05,000 --> 00:45:06,800
But when I looked at your face,

796
00:45:07,900 --> 00:45:10,000
I actually ended up feeling bad for you.

797
00:45:11,900 --> 00:45:14,466
I wasn't upset about
being told I have bad taste.

798
00:45:15,600 --> 00:45:17,566
I was just afraid you'd agree with them.

799
00:45:18,800 --> 00:45:22,400
Afraid that one day you'd look
at me and regret your choice.

800
00:45:23,933 --> 00:45:25,500
Honestly, I've been so tired lately.

801
00:45:26,366 --> 00:45:27,400
The shop is opening soon,

802
00:45:27,933 --> 00:45:28,933
there's so much work,

803
00:45:29,700 --> 00:45:31,060
and the future is still uncertain.

804
00:45:32,100 --> 00:45:34,566
But every time I look over
and see you by my side,

805
00:45:35,766 --> 00:45:37,566
it feels like all my
worries just fade away.

806
00:45:38,266 --> 00:45:39,266
Me too.

807
00:45:40,333 --> 00:45:41,733
Since I've had you,

808
00:45:42,800 --> 00:45:44,366
my life has gotten a lot louder,

809
00:45:45,100 --> 00:45:46,100
more chaotic,

810
00:45:46,533 --> 00:45:47,533
more tiring,

811
00:45:48,800 --> 00:45:50,466
but also so damn much happier.

812
00:45:53,966 --> 00:45:56,776
(Next Episode) Lying breaks the fourth precept.
(from The Five Precepts of Buddhism)

813
00:45:56,800 --> 00:45:58,066
Next time, can you please

814
00:45:58,400 --> 00:45:59,400
just tell me the truth?

815
00:45:59,733 --> 00:46:02,100
I won't be mad if you have a good reason.

816
00:46:05,900 --> 00:46:06,900
Hia?

817
00:46:07,766 --> 00:46:08,766
Hia?

818
00:46:10,100 --> 00:46:11,100
It hurts.

819
00:46:13,333 --> 00:46:14,700
It hurts, Erng.
